  moses,3,18,"And I, the Lord God, said unto mine Only Begotten, that it was not good that the man should be alone; wherefore, I will make an help meet for him.","36:49:TG Jesus Christ, Divine Sonship.|95:100:TG Family, Eternal.|128:132:Gen. 2:18; Abr. 5:14."
