  moses,4,4,"And he became Satan, yea, even the devil, the father of all lies, to deceive and to blind men, and to lead them captive at his will, even as many as would not hearken unto my voice.","14:19:Moses 1:12.|35:40:TG Devil.|60:64:2 Ne. 2:18; D&C 10:25. TG Honesty; Lying.|69:76:1 Thes. 3:5; D&C 29:39 (39–40, 47). TG Deceit.|112:119:TG Bondage, Spiritual.|159:166:TG Disobedience."
