  moses,4,6,"And Satan put it into the heart of the serpent, (for he had drawn away many after him,) and he sought also to beguile Eve, for he knew not the mind of God, wherefore he sought to destroy the world.","4:9:TG Devil.|71:75:D&C 29:36.|110:117:TG Honesty.|130:138:John 16:3 (1–3).|143:147:1 Cor. 2:16. TG Mind."
