  moses,5,5,"And he gave unto them commandments, that they should worship the Lord their God, and should offer the firstlings of their flocks, for an offering unto the Lord. And Adam was obedient unto the commandments of the Lord.","53:60:TG Worship.|102:112:Ex. 13:12 (12–13); Num. 18:17; Mosiah 2:3. TG Firstborn.|122:128:Moses 5:19 (19–20).|174:182:TG Obedience."
