  moses,7,28,"And it came to pass that the God of heaven looked upon the residue of the people, and he wept; and Enoch bore record of it, saying: How is it that the heavens weep, and shed forth their tears as the rain upon the mountains?","59:66:Moro. 7:32; Moses 7:20."
