  moses,7,36,"Wherefore, I can stretch forth mine hands and hold all the creations which I have made; and mine eye can pierce them also, and among all the workmanship of mine hands there has not been so great wickedness as among thy brethren.","59:68:D&C 38:2; 88:41; Moses 1:35 (35–37). TG God, Omniscience of.|195:205:Gen. 6:5 (5–6); 3 Ne. 9:9; Morm. 4:12 (10–12); D&C 112:23; Moses 8:22 (22, 28–30)."
